ox Put to Rout<br />--Frog Chorus<br />--Performing Mice<br />--The Clay Scholar<br />--Flowers of Illusion<br />--Dwarf<br />--Bird<br />--Princess Lotus<br />--The Girl in Green<br />--Duck Justice<br />--Big Sneeze<br />--Steel Shirt<br />--Fox Trouble<br />--Lust Punished by Foxes<br />--Mountain City<br />--A Cure for Marital Strife<br />--A Prank<br />--Adultery and Enlightenment<br />--Up His Sleeve<br />--Silver Above Beauty<br />--The Antique Lute<br />--Waiting Room for Death<br />--Rouge<br />--The Southern Wutong-Spirit<br />--Sunset<br />--The Male Concubine<br />--Coral<br />--Mutton Fat and Pig Blood<br />--Dung-Beetle Dumplings<br />--Stir-Fry<br /><br /><i>Author's Preface<br />Glossary<br />Maps<br />Finding List<br />Further Reading<br />Notes</i></span>
