    <a title="Peiyao Yan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/91643111-peiyao-yan"><img alt="Peiyao Yan" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2701775104?book_show_action=true">Feb 03, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Peiyao Yan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Peiyao Yan" href="/user/show/91643111-peiyao-yan">Peiyao Yan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780887101144" href="/book/show/1560601.Strange_Stories_from_a_Chinese_Studio">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2701775104" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14193087066788876752">The author combined the clips he heard on the street in tea house, and formed a long story on his own. The story is composed by different kinds of ghost. I think that it should be counted as a tall tale, because that the ghosts are something supernatural. The ghosts are described with really strong power and types of abilities. Those characteristics are meant to show more about the tragedies happened those days. The stories are short and most of them are about love between family, friends and lo</span>
  <span id="freeText14193087066788876752" style="display:none">The author combined the clips he heard on the street in tea house, and formed a long story on his own. The story is composed by different kinds of ghost. I think that it should be counted as a tall tale, because that the ghosts are something supernatural. The ghosts are described with really strong power and types of abilities. Those characteristics are meant to show more about the tragedies happened those days. The stories are short and most of them are about love between family, friends and lovers. <br />It can be a great choice to introduce to my students on a reading class. I can ask them to pick their favorite clips of the story, or act the story out to class. The story is not scary although it is about the ghosts. It shows more about the emotion between people and the spiritual pain they suffered. And it formed a happy ending of the story. <br />You can also find some similar clips of the stories, but each character has its own significant characteristics. Also, the story is based on the normal life. I’ve seen a lot of details it mentioned in the texts and some of the clips are still not available to explain its scientific principles. </span>
  <a data-text-id="14193087066788876752" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


