          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A man eager to climb famous mountains must have the patience to follow a winding path. A man eager to eat bear's paw must have the patience to simmer it slowly. A man eager to watch the moonlight must have the patience to wait until midnight. A man eager to see a beautiful woman must have the patience to let her finish her toilette. Reading requires patience too.&rdquo;</span>
